      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLESSED RAIN (4) is a sprinter who thrives over these shorter races. Kept coming to fill the minor placings over 390m at Warrnambool (22.50) in a Free For All. Solid record here at this trip including four wins. Boasts four wins from five starts out of this box. Capable of going well again. PAW BASTOW (1) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish 3 lengths back in second (22.32) at Warrnambool in a Grade 5 over 390m. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. PAW ESTRELLA (3) boasts strong form at this course and distance having won three times from five starts. Recorded a 2.75 lengths win (23.27) in a Grade 5 last time at Horsham. Looks well placed here and among the chances. DOONGALLA ROCKET (2) was below best last time at Ballarat (25.86) in a Special conditions H, finishing a 11 length sixth. Has two wins already from this draw.",
